 rollback instead of the\nexpensive dbmsManager.emptyDatabase() truncate-all run per test method.\n\nTests whose reads go through raw jdbcTemplate SQL (or whose write happens via\nsession.doWork on the shared connection) get an explicit entityManager.flush()\nso those reads see the un-committed session writes within the same transaction.\n\nMeasured ~52% reduction in per-class execution time on the 6 separable converted\nclasses in a shared-context run (each ~halves, consistent with eliminating one\nemptyDatabase() truncate per test method).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"bc5ea1f4d925e5f2e1e0dfa89b304037ac681300","tree_id":"246e1be956bdb170a45af72d0cf642b90028c837","timestamp":"2026-05-27T18:56:22Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core